戞字的汉语字典释义

[①]［jiá］
［《廣韻》古黠切，入黠，見。］
亦作“戞1”。“拮2”的被通假字。
(1)戟。《说文·戈部》：“戛，戟也。”一说为长矛。
(2)常礼，常法。
(3)敲击；触及。
(4)刮平。
(5)指研磨。
(6)艰难费力。见“戛戛”。
(7)怪异，独特。
(8)象声词。见“戛戛”、“戛然”。
(9)见“戛服”。

Chinese dictionary definition of words
[①]［jiá］
["Guangyun" cut from ancient points, enter the points, see. ]
Also known as "戞1". "Jia 2" was passed falsely.
(1) Halberd. "Said Wen Ge Bu": "G, halberd." One is a spear.
(2) Regular etiquette, regular law.
(3) Percussion; touch.
(4) Scrape it.
(5) Refers to grinding.
(6) Difficulty and laborious. See "Can Ga".
(7) Weird and unique.
(8) Onomatopoeia. See "Jan Jia" and "Jan Ran".
(9) See "Jifu".
